By Mike Odiegwu, Yenagoa Minister of State for Petroleum Minister and former Governor of Bayelsa State, Chief Timipre Sylva, has delivered his Brass Local Government Area to the All Progressives Congress (APC) and its candidate, Chief David Lyon. Lyon polled 23,831 votes to defeat his counterpart in the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), Senator Douye Diri, who scored 10, 410
Brass has a total registered voters of 67,355. Out of the number 35,657 were accredited to vote at the poll.